				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">MMC3 IRQs are triggered on the first rising edge of PPU A12 in a given scanline (it has a buffer of sorts to filter out rapid sequences), and the PPU does not access the sprite pattern table until cycle 260 - this would explain your timing problems.
<br />
<br />(cycle 260 is when the PPU outputs and latches the address; cycle 261 is when the actual read takes place)</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
