						<div class="postbody">Awesome.  I suspected as much after re-checking BT's doc (it says the first sprite pattern is fetched on memory access 131 -- cycle 260).
<br />
<br />Anyway... just tried it out in my emu... and it seems to have worked ^^.  Wolverine and Recca are both running great.
<br />
<br />Thanks again Q
<br />
<br />edit - seems like this is what is needed to make Kick Master's title screen work as well.  Neato ^^</div>

